<p class="lead">The content halves pattern contains two, equal-width content columns. There is the option to have a heading above the columns and a full-width background colour.</p>

<h2>Rules for content halves</h2>

<ul>
	<li>Accordions may be used in either column.</li>
    <li>The background colour must be either white or grey. Add the class <code>sta-grey-light</code> for a grey background.</li>
    <li>Add the classes <code>padding-top</code> and <code>padding-bottom</code> to add vertical padding. This must be used when applying a background colour.</li>
</ul>

